{"tid":1898581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住而家係軍政府狀態，所以根本就冇派錢vs裝甲車問題","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T07:34:34.000Z","uid":124636,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f4a99a4f0523211639f091bdee343fa168272c","tid":1898581,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"軍政府會因為你議會反對而唔批資源比差役咩？之前黑警d OT費有諮詢過議會咩？係唔會架<br />\n<br />\n所以根本冇派錢vs裝甲車依個問題，因為你地收唔收10000萬，軍政府點死都死到d錢去比班黑警，連登仔唔好比人分化啦<br />\n<br />\n黃營每人多一萬，max.計即係成個陣營多200億，對成個抗爭點會冇幫助？<br />\n<br />\n泛民議員點做就要考佢地智慧喇，朱凱迪就示範左其中一個方向<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸： 反對綑綁「回水一萬」與「警察加錢」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898525</a><br />\n<br />\n全民派錢應成獨立議案以加快審議 絕不應與預算案掛鈎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898500</a>"},{"pid":"94fd670a597877854eecbc8606f2bcbfe7895785","tid":1898581,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"7fe5e8c9ab1af1b7ad3900dd58cc7ccb9ca68c6d","tid":1898581,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報道<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=3ebe3849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&h=f38fff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649